on attemptHeal me
  [  0] getprop 777 ............................. <pHealDelayCounter>
  [  3] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <pHealDelayCounter>
  [  5] extcall 553 ............................. counter(pHealDelayCounter)
  [  8] getprop 777 ............................. <pHealDelayCounter>
  [ 11] getobjprop 552 .......................... <pHealDelayCounter.fin>
  [ 14] jmpifz [ 82] ............................ if pHealDelayCounter.fin then
  [ 17] getprop 778 ............................. <pRemainingHitpoints>
  [ 20] pushzero ................................ <0>
  [ 21] gt ...................................... <pRemainingHitpoints > 0>
  [ 22] jmpifz [ 64] ............................ if pRemainingHitpoints > 0 then / else
  [ 25] getprop 778 ............................. <pRemainingHitpoints>
  [ 28] getprop 776 ............................. <pHealAmount>
  [ 31] sub ..................................... <pRemainingHitpoints - pHealAmount>
