  [ 35] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [ 37] getchainedprop 57 ....................... <me.id>
  [ 39] getchainedprop 58 ....................... <me.id.bigMe>
  [ 41] getprop 776 ............................. <pHealAmount>
