  [  8] pushzero ................................ <0>
  [  9] gt ...................................... <pRemainingHitpoints > 0>
  [ 10] jmpifz [ 20] ............................ if pRemainingHitpoints > 0 then
  [ 13] getlocal 0 .............................. <numOfMedikits>
  [ 15] pushint8 1 .............................. <1>
